title: how/where bts would kiss you!
body:
↳ prompt: bts x reader - how/where they would kiss you.


jin / kim seokjin:

jin is a kind of old-fashioned guy but at the same time a great lover of romance - he’s more likely to kiss his s/o’s hand while having a flirtatious glint in his eyes. he’d probably do it to see his s/o’s response and whether they were blushing or not.

suga / min yoongi:

yoongi isn’t the most affectionate guy in the world but he always wants to make sure that you know how much you mean to him, he’s likely to kiss your cheek after probably staring at you for a long time in awe or lowkey whippedness.

j-hope / jung hoseok:

hobi, being hobi, is more likely to kiss the crook of your neck after back-hugging you. since hoseok is quite the clingy person and loves touching others - especially his loved ones - he’d also do it repeatedly since you defo know he wouldn’t let go of you.

rm / kim namjoon:

namjoon would kiss you on the forehead since he’s probably definitley taller than you and he finds you super cute and when he’s in his soft mode, he’d love to just swoop down for a second and leave a small peck on your head.

jimin / park jimin:

so like j-hope, jimin is super touchy and is probably the sweetest and softest out of all the members!! jimin would probably do an eskimo kiss because it means that him and his s/o are super close and he can look directly in your eyes, he’d also do it a lot and probably in private because he would want to show his affection for you and you only.

v / kim taehyung:

so tae is a hard one since tae is all about experimenting so i don’t think tae has a specific kissing style, it really depends on his mood since when he’s happy he’s more likely to kiss you on the cheek whereas when he’s feeling a surge of love for his s/o - either way taehyung’s got a heart of love and it’s waiting for you!

jungkook / jeon jeongguk:

alright bois jungkook is a bit of a risk taker so jungkook loves expressing his love and he also loves showing off his relationship so don’t be shocked if jungkook kisses you right on the lips! jungkook is a bit like jin too, he gets high off seeing your reaction so if you start blushing don’t get shocked if he does it again or tease you for it!

title: fate hates us.
body:
by colourdark

So what if Min Yoongi was his roommate; that didn’t mean Jimin couldn’t hate him.

And so what if Min Yoongi was ridiculously hot; that didn’t mean Jimin wanted to fuck him, or that he was even interested despite what his friends said.

And yeah, Jimin was desperately trying to hide the fact that he worked as a stripper from his roommate; it didn’t mean he cared about his opinion.

None of that meant that Park Jimin wouldn’t definitely, absolutely, undoubtedly, always hate Min Yoongi.
